jobDescription: Ready to join a well-known, established government organization? Located in the San Francisco area and paying up to $65,000 currently looking for an Analyst II who would be responsible for quality control, data reporting, producing reports, and administering surveys. This company is looking for someone with 3-5 years of experience, a degree in social sciences, economics, math, business or related fields, and proficiency with Microsoft Suite: Excel, Word, Access, and Outlook. The management team looks forward to working closely with you to ensure your success and career growth. This opportunity is looking to hire now!
